## å…¬å…±å‡½æ•°ï¼ˆç®€çŸ­è¯´æ˜ï¼‰ ğŸ“š

- `generate_signature(appid, secret_key, url, method='GET', body=None, query=None, timestamp=None, nonce=None, ends_with_secret_key=False)`ï¼šç”ŸæˆåŸå§‹ç­¾åå­—ç¬¦ä¸²ä¸ç­¾åï¼ˆè¿”å› `raw_str`, `signature`, `url`ï¼‰ã€‚

- `generate_signature_header(appid, secret_key, url, method='GET', body=None, query=None, ends_with_secret_key=False, with_hash_name=True, pair_value=False)`ï¼šåœ¨ `generate_signature` åŸºç¡€ä¸Šç”Ÿæˆç”¨äº HTTP header çš„ç­¾åå­—ç¬¦ä¸²ï¼ˆå¯é€‰å¸¦ `HMAC-SHA256 ` å‰ç¼€æˆ–é”®å€¼å¯¹å½¢å¼ï¼‰ã€‚

- `verify_signature(appid, secret_key, url, method='GET', body=None, query=None, timestamp=None, nonce=None, ends_with_secret_key=False, verify_timestamp=True, timestamp_valid_time=300, signature='')`ï¼šéªŒè¯ç­¾åæ˜¯å¦åŒ¹é…å¹¶å¯é€‰æ ¡éªŒæ—¶é—´æˆ³ï¼Œè¿”å› `code/message` ç­‰ä¿¡æ¯ã€‚

- `verify_signature_header(url, method='GET', body=None, query=None, timestamp=None, nonce=None, ends_with_secret_key=False, verify_timestamp=True, timestamp_valid_time=300, signature='', verify_hash_name=True, with_hash_name=True, pair_value=False, header_value='', get_secretkey_by_appid=None)`ï¼šè§£æå¹¶éªŒè¯ç­¾åå¤´ï¼Œ`get_secretkey_by_appid` ä¸ºå¼‚æ­¥å‡½æ•°ï¼Œæ¥æ”¶ `appid` å¹¶è¿”å›å¯¹åº”çš„ `secret_key`ã€‚

---

## ç¤ºä¾‹ âœ¨

```python
import asyncio
from api_signature import (
    generate_signature,
    generate_signature_header,
    verify_signature,
    verify_signature_header,
)

appid = "appid"
secret_key = "secret_key"

async def main():
    # ç”Ÿæˆç­¾åï¼ˆGETï¼‰
    sig = await generate_signature(appid, secret_key, "/path", "GET")
    print("generate_signature ->", sig)

    # ç”Ÿæˆå¸¦ header çš„ç­¾åï¼ˆPOSTï¼‰
    header = await generate_signature_header(
        appid, secret_key, "/path", "POST", {"a": "a", "b": 1}, {"_t": "1234567890"}
    )
    print("generate_signature_header ->", header)

    # éªŒè¯ç­¾åï¼ˆç›´æ¥ä¼  signatureï¼‰
    vs = await verify_signature(
        url="/path",
        appid=appid,
        secret_key=secret_key,
        nonce="IsJRqILi",
        timestamp="1766335905",
        signature="FCAA034551D699945D5B6FD44562D977B0E924DDE8DA4732D5E8F53A3B929141",
    )
    print("verify_signature ->", vs)

    # éªŒè¯ç­¾åå¤´ï¼ˆéœ€æä¾›å¼‚æ­¥å›è°ƒæ ¹æ® appid è·å– secret keyï¼‰
    async def get_secret(appid_):
        return secret_key

    vsh = await verify_signature_header(
        url="/path",
        method="POST",
        body={"a": "a", "b": 1},
        query={"_t": "1234567890"},
        header_value="HMAC-SHA256 appid:1766336579:Ob0Fy5Xd:D6F3973B00B7463EDA081284775D4770B60430E620E9C804D8B267290AC5BD4D",
        get_secretkey_by_appid=get_secret,
    )
    print("verify_signature_header ->", vsh)

asyncio.run(main())
```
